Summary: Biochemical reaction from aripiprazole to dehydroaripiprazole. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2D6, CYP3A5 or CYP3A4.
Biochemical reaction from aripiprazole to aripiprazole metabolite DM-1451. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP3A4 or CYP2D6.
Biochemical reaction from aripiprazole to 1-(2,3-dichlorophenyl)piperazine. This interaction is catalyzed by CYP3A4.
Biochemical reaction from N-hydroxymethyl aripiprazole to aripiprazole, formaldehyde.
Biochemical reaction from aripiprazole lauroxil to N-hydroxymethyl aripiprazole, lauric acid.
Transport from aripiprazole to aripiprazole. This interaction is catalyzed by ABCB1.
